title: Don't Chase The Glory, Work Hard, and Be Satisfied with Tyler Deeb
description: No matter how successful you become, when your insecurities are the motivation of your work, you will never be satisfied. Tyler Deeb, Founder of Misc. Goods Co., joins us this week to share his creative journey, experience as a designer, and the joy and pain of launching his own business.
